  "excerpt": "Many people assume that the reason many people blog is because they enjoy having  all  the answers.",
  "image": "",
  "readTime": "1 min",
  "content": [
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Many people assume that the reason many people blog is because they enjoy having ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "all",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " the answers.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "That writing fuels their ego, satiating their endless desire for pretentious edification.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I’m not so sure that’s the ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "only",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " reason to regularly write.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Because the best reason to write—consistently, honestly, the best way you know how—is to have an opinion.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Not to have all the answers, and not to always be right.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "But to know what you’re thinking. What you’re feeling. What you believe in, and what’s important to you.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "What makes writing a blog so gratifying is that it’s a totally unrestricted way to express yourself, to share your point of view, and (sometimes) to let your thoughts be heard.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Free therapy.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}